data.description: Welcome home to this 3 bed, 2 bath ranch on a cul-de-sac lot! Complete with a vinyl plank entrance area for welcoming guests, a large living room with vaulted ceilings & a gas fireplace. Great for hosting & entertaining! The kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, vinyl plank floors, a separate breakfast area, a breakfast bar & a pantry. Just off the living room is a separate dining room or flex space. Split bedroom plan. Large owners suite with vaulted ceilings, a walk-in closet, a separate soaking tub & shower, with updated ceramic tile floors in both bathrooms. Laundry floor is also updated with vinyl plank. New roof 2020, New HVAC 2022, extended side driveway for larger vehicles as needed. Come be a part of Georgia's Hollywood; about 20 minutes from the Covington square where you can dine at fine restaurants & shop at specialty boutiques. Come be a part of all this sweet town has to offer.
